Uses of Package
com.flexganttfx.view.timeline

  • Packages that use com.flexganttfx.view.timeline 
    Package Description
    com.flexganttfx.view
    The main Gantt chart controls.
    com.flexganttfx.view.graphics
    The various graphics controls that are used for rendering the Gantt chart.
    com.flexganttfx.view.timeline
    The timeline control, which consists of the dateline and the eventline child controls.
    com.flexganttfx.view.util
    Various utility classes.
  • Classes in com.flexganttfx.view.timeline used by com.flexganttfx.view 
    Class and Description
    Timeline
    The timeline control is a container for the Dateline and the Eventline.
  • Classes in com.flexganttfx.view.timeline used by com.flexganttfx.view.graphics 
    Class and Description
    Timeline
    The timeline control is a container for the Dateline and the Eventline.
  • Classes in com.flexganttfx.view.timeline used by com.flexganttfx.view.timeline 
    Class and Description
    Dateline
    The dateline is a control that displays the actual dates (Mo, Tu, We, ...) in cells in one or more rows.
    DatelineCell
    Each row / scale in the Dateline consists of several cells.
    DatelineScrollingEvent
    A special event type used for informing the application about horizontal scrolling within the dateline.
    Eventline
    The eventline is a control that displays time cursors and other information that might be relevant for all rows in the Gantt chart.
    Timeline
    The timeline control is a container for the Dateline and the Eventline.
    Timeline.ZoomMode
    An enum used to control the way that zooming operations will happen.
  • Classes in com.flexganttfx.view.timeline used by com.flexganttfx.view.util 
    Class and Description
    Timeline
    The timeline control is a container for the Dateline and the Eventline.
